The FCO is advising that if you live in the UK and are currently travelling abroad, you should to return to the UK now, where and while there are still commercial routes available. There are currently no commercial options to leave North Macedonia.
The British Embassy Skopje is issuing regular updates on Facebook and Twitter with the latest available information.
Further information
See additional advice on making travel plans to return to the UK, or what to do if you cannot depart immediately.
